  -> L3-C60-pentagons, BIG-C60-atoms-60, ENERGY-grid-60Hz, L3-benzene, ENERGY-solar-60cell, L4-amino-acids
@F L3-C60-pentagons = sigma :: molecule [10*]
  "C60 오각형 면 수"
  <- L3-water, L2-fcc-slip-systems, L3-C60
