#   - existing MILL-PX-A8, HEXA-NS, HEXA-BSD, HEXA-POINCARE-* prefixes
#     (all preserved; this shard uses N6HIST-* prefix to avoid collision)
#
# Falsifier-active markers retained per source report; OBSTRUCTION_DOCUMENTED
# verdicts reproduced verbatim (no upgrading to PASS).
#
# Millennium tally as carried forward by source corpus: 0/7 unchanged.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

