  → "  95% CI on r at n=15 is ~±0.5 — partial-correlation absolute values are not tight"
  → "  cartoon excluded (iter-38 outlier in axis-13)"
  → "  flat excluded (D=2 in axis-13 by convention)"
  → "  calabi6 excluded (D=6, no axis-13 D=3 baseline)"
  → "  Toy σ²=64 lattice unchanged across all 3 axes"
  → "  own#11 violation: 0 (no Clay BT 'resolution' claim attempted)"

@R sim-3-axis-cumulative-state :: meta [4]
  → "Post-46-iter-cascade analysis shard — pure information-theoretic synthesis"
  → "Axes structured: 15 (axis-13/14/15 information characterized)"
  → "Topologies in 3-way table: 15 D=3"
  → "Loop self-correction: 0 (analysis-only, no new probes)"
  → "Output: this shard at atlas/atlas.append.sim-3-axis-information-structure-2026-04-28.n6"

