@C sim-scale-up-AXIS-14-15-VERDICT :: meta [4!]
  → "★★★★★ Verdict on iter-50 / iter-69 scale invariance question:"
  → ""
  → "  ORIGINAL QUESTIONS (asked at task start):"
  → "    Q1: Does iter-50 'D=2 << D=3 << D=6' (r=0.99) hold at σ²>64?"
